data.description: Welcome home to this light & bright beautifully updated 4 bedroom home nestled in Harriet Creek. This home is located in the highly sought after NWISD school district. It offers a very spacious living with laminate wood look throughout. 4 large sized bedrooms that provide comfort for everyone.The very large primary suite is a private retreat complete with a beautiful ensuite bathroom with oversized shower, double sinks & large walk in closet.The open living area flows seamlessly from the cozy family room to the newer updated kitchen with granite counters and ample storage.It's perfect for hosting gatherings. Second living and dining downstairs. Beautiful curb appeal. Location is ideal with shopping, dining and the Texas Motor Speedway close by.All 3 schools, pool and park located close by. Easy access to 114 and 35W to Fort Worth and Dallas. Short drive to airport.NEW HVAC & sprinkler system.
